instructions: Hard boil eggs and chop, In a bowl, mix chopped eggs with mayonnaise and mustard, Spread on bread, Top with lettuce, Cut in half and serve

ingredients: Pork shoulder, BBQ sauce, Burger buns, Coleslaw
instructions: Slow cook pork shoulder until tender, Shred and mix with BBQ sauce, Serve on burger buns topped with coleslaw, Enjoy with pickles on the side

ingredients: Banana, Peanut butter, Almond milk, Honey, Ice
instructions: In a blender, combine banana, peanut butter, almond milk, honey, and ice, Blend until smooth, Pour into a glass and enjoy as a nutritious breakfast or snack

ingredients: Zucchini, Ground turkey, Tomato sauce, Cheese, Italian seasoning
instructions: Preheat oven to 180°C, Halve zucchini and scoop out the center, Cook ground turkey with tomato sauce and seasonings, Fill zucchini halves with the mixture, Top with cheese and bake for 20 minutes

ingredients: Quinoa, Bell peppers, Zucchini, Olive oil, Balsamic vinegar
instructions: Cook quinoa according to package instructions, Toss chopped vegetables in olive oil and balsamic vinegar, Roast in the oven for 25 minutes, Mix roasted vegetables with quinoa and serve warm

ingredients: Salmon fillet, Teriyaki sauce, Sesame seeds, Green onions
instructions: Preheat oven to 200°C, Marinate salmon in teriyaki sauce for 30 minutes, Place on a baking sheet and bake for 15 minutes, Garnish with sesame seeds and chopped green onions before serving

ingredients: Pasta, Cherry tomatoes, Mozzarella balls, Basil, Olive oil
instructions: Cook pasta according to package instructions, Drain and let cool, In a bowl, combine pasta, halved cherry tomatoes, mozzarella balls, and basil, Drizzle with olive oil, Toss gently and serve

ingredients: Beef, Broccoli, Soy sauce, Garlic, Rice
instructions: Slice beef thinly and marinate in soy sauce, In a pan, stir-fry beef until browned, Add broccoli and cook until tender, Serve over cooked rice

ingredients: Peaches, Sugar, Flour, Butter, Baking powder
instructions: Preheat oven to 180°C, Slice peaches and toss with sugar, In a bowl, mix flour, sugar, baking powder, and melted butter, Pour batter over peaches in a baking dish, Bake for 30-35 minutes until golden

ingredients: Bananas, Oats, Eggs, Milk, Baking powder
instructions: In a bowl, mash bananas, Mix in oats, eggs, and milk, Add baking powder, Cook on a skillet until golden, Serve with maple syrup

ingredients: Banana, Cocoa powder, Almond milk, Peanut butter, Honey
instructions: In a blender, combine banana, cocoa powder, almond milk, peanut butter, and honey, Blend until smooth, Pour into a glass and serve immediately

ingredients: Lasagna noodles, Ricotta cheese, Spinach, Marinara sauce, Mozzarella cheese
instructions: Preheat oven to 180°C, Cook lasagna noodles according to package instructions, In a bowl, mix ricotta, spinach, and seasonings, Layer noodles, ricotta mixture, marinara, and mozzarella in a baking dish, Repeat layers, Bake for 30-35 minutes until bubbly

ingredients: Rice, Coconut milk, Sugar, Cinnamon, Raisins
instructions: In a pot, combine rice, coconut milk, sugar, and cinnamon, Cook over low heat until rice is tender, Stir in raisins, Serve warm or chilled as a delicious dessert

ingredients: Pizza dough, BBQ sauce, Chicken, Red onions, Mozzarella cheese
instructions: Preheat oven to 220°C, Roll out pizza dough and spread BBQ sauce on top, Add cooked chicken, sliced red onions, and mozzarella, Bake for 15-20 minutes until crust is golden, Slice and serve hot

recipe_name: Sweet Potato and Black Bean Tacos
ingredients: Sweet potatoes, Black beans, Corn tortillas, Avocado, Salsa
instructions: Roast cubed sweet potatoes in the oven until tender, Warm black beans on the stove, Fill corn tortillas with sweet potatoes and beans, Top with avocado and salsa, Serve with lime wedges

ingredients: Avocado, Cocoa powder, Maple syrup, Vanilla extract
instructions: In a blender, combine ripe avocados, cocoa powder, maple syrup, and vanilla, Blend until smooth and creamy, Chill in the refrigerator for 30 minutes, Serve in bowls with optional toppings like berries

ingredients: Chicken breast, Olive oil, Herbs, Garlic, Lemon
instructions: Preheat oven to 200°C, Rub chicken breast with olive oil, minced garlic, and herbs, Bake for 25-30 minutes until cooked through, Let rest before slicing, Serve with a side salad
